definitions.definition: A hamlet and civil parish in South Gloucestershire district, Gloucestershire , England ( OS grid ref ST7686 ) .
A town in the United Counties of Prescott and Russell , Ontario , Canada , named after Lord Hawkesbury .
A river , the Hawkesbury River , in New South Wales , Australia , named after Lord Hawkesbury (as in Ontario).
A local government area , the City of Hawkesbury , located near Sydney in New South Wales , Australia , named after the river.
